# GTN1828 — Automated Waisteband Attachment System

**Role:** Lead Mechanical Engineer

Led the reverse engineering and mechanical design of an automated waisteband attachment machine. Created complete SolidWorks assemblies and documentation to support manufacturing and assembly. The machine automates the folding process to assist operators to increase productivity and decrease injury, such as carpal tunnel.

